### ============================================
### MMOS API Example
### Execute Workflow
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### ============================================
### Execute Workflow
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/execute
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowId": "workflow.pipeline.multimedia-content",

  "runtime": {
    "provider": "openai",
    "model": "gpt-4.1"
  },

  "input": {
    "topic": "Artificial Intelligence",
    "language": "en"
  }
}

###

### ============================================
### Get Execution Status
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Get Execution Logs
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Pause Execution
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/pause
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Resume Execution
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Cancel Execution
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### List Executions
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/executions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Get Execution Artifacts
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/artifacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Retry Failed Execution
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}